The '''''Mallixer''''' was a [[Starship/Legends|ship]] that belonged to [[Jaxa]] and [[Bettle]], two [[Smuggler/Legends|smugglers]] who lived in the [[Time/Legends|time]] of the early part of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. The ''Mallixer'' was used for smuggling, and quite often (as is to be expected in such operations) narrowly escaped destruction, or worse, confiscation.

